dc_creator_sm: US Bureau of the Census: http://www.census.gov
dc_description_s: This service presents various population statistics from Census 2000, including total population, population density, racial counts, and more. The map service presents statistics at the county level. This is a sample service hosted by ESRI, powered by ArcGIS Server. ESRI reserves the right to change or remove this service at any time and without notice.
